@@TJvDataEmbedded.Data
Description:
This property contains the data embedded in the component. Use this property to retrieve the data, and use the editor to modify the data on design time. Attention, any modification made in runtime won't be saved in the executable! The data must be modified on design time only!

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvDataEmbedded.Size
Description:
This property specifies the size of the data embedded with the component.

